                            <comment id="486918" author="adilger" created="Sat, 7 Feb 2026 23:47:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;After patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/63451&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/63451&lt;/a&gt; (&quot;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18448&quot; title=&quot;Read Directory page on open.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-18448&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-18448&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; llite: disable dir read on open by default&quot;) landed this issue has been avoided. Shaun Tancheff has patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/63437&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/63437&lt;/a&gt; (&quot;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19774&quot; title=&quot;sanity test_428: crash on aarch64 - invoked oom-killer&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-19774&quot;&gt;LU-19774&lt;/a&gt; llite: limit dir_read_on_open for non-4k clients&quot;) to further limit this to only clients with large PAGE_SIZE.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="484280" author="adilger" created="Fri, 16 Jan 2026 22:56:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patches that are hitting this failure cannot pass by retesting, and must be rebased to get a fix.&#160; Please see &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19767&quot; title=&quot;sanity test_398b: timeout&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-19767&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-19767&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for details.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="483579" author="arshad512" created="Tue, 13 Jan 2026 03:54:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 on master: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/2941e3cd-3a2d-4410-a9b9-864f718afc81&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/2941e3cd-3a2d-4410-a9b9-864f718afc81&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="483547" author="adilger" created="Mon, 12 Jan 2026 21:36:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It looks like this may be the same problem as &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19767&quot; title=&quot;sanity test_398b: timeout&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-19767&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-19767&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, which is causing timeouts in sanity test_398b on aarch64 (also doing a bunch of IO).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
